pokedexEntries.gold: The aroma that rises from its petals contains a substance that calms aggressive feelings.
pokedexEntries.silver: Meganium's breath has the power to revive dead grass and plants. It can make them healthy again.
pokedexEntries.crystal: Anyone who stands beside it becomes refreshed, just as if they were relaxing in a sunny forest.
pokedexEntries.ruby: The fragrance of Meganium's flower soothes and calms emotions. In battle, this Pokémon gives off more of its becalming scent to blunt the foe's fighting spirit.
